msgstr "Rather, by saying this you just teach Dhamma: "

msgctxt "mn139:8.4"
msgid "‘Anuyogo ca kho sadukkho eso dhammo saupaghāto saupāyāso sapariḷāho; "
msgstr "‘The indulgence is a principle beset by pain, harm, stress, and fever, and it is the wrong way.’ "

msgctxt "mn139:8.5"
msgid "micchāpaṭipadā’ti—"
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn139:8.6"
msgid "iti vadaṃ dhammameva deseti. "
msgstr " "

