#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc16
msgctxt "mn139:8.26"
msgid "‘Yesaṃ kesañci bhavasaṃyojanaṃ pahīnaṃ, sabbe te adukkhā anupaghātā anupāyāsā apariḷāhā sammāpaṭipannā’ti—"
