#. REF: nya14, sc31
msgctxt "mn139:14.1"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, ‘saraṇañca dhammaṃ jānissāma, araṇañca dhammaṃ jānissāma; "
msgstr "So you should train like this: ‘We shall know the principles beset by conflict and the principles free of conflict. "

msgctxt "mn139:14.2"
msgid "saraṇañca dhammaṃ ñatvā araṇañca dhammaṃ ñatvā araṇapaṭipadaṃ paṭipajjissāmā’ti evañhi vo, bhikkhave, sikkhitabbaṃ. "
msgstr "Knowing this, we will practice the way free of conflict.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "mn139:14.3"
msgid "Subhūti ca pana, bhikkhave, kulaputto araṇapaṭipadaṃ paṭipanno”ti. "
msgstr "And, mendicants, Subhūti, the gentleman, practices the way of non-conflict.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc32
msgctxt "mn139:14.4"
msgid "Idamavoca bhagavā. "
msgstr "That is what the Buddha said. "

msgctxt "mn139:14.5"
msgid "Attamanā te bhikkhū bhagavato bhāsitaṃ abhinandunti. "
msgstr "Satisfied, the mendicants were happy with what the Buddha said. "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "mn139:14.6"
msgid "Araṇavibhaṅgasuttaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ navamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

